extendedInfo.description: According to Chinese Astrology, your birth year tells you more than just your age. Find out what your Chinese zodiac sign reveals about you now!Chinese Horoscope features:â â â  DREAMBOOK â â â  NEW!- Chinese Full Horoscope- Chinese Yearly Horoscope- Chinese Daily HoroscopeChinese horoscopes for Rat, Ox, Tiger, Rabbit, Dragon, Snake, Horse, Sheep, Monkey, Rooster, Dog, Boar.The lunar calendar has a sixty year cycle. In the Chinesehoroscope, the five basic elements of Metal, Water, Wood, Fire and Earth, which make up all matter, are combined with the twelve animal signs of Rat, Ox, Tiger, Rabbit, Dragon, Snake, Horse, Lamb, Monkey, Rooster, Dog and Pig to form the sixty year cycle. One's Chinese horoscope is based on which lunar year in thissixty year cycle one was born.

reviews.title: A breakup letter:
reviews.comment: I\'m sorry, Chinese Horoscope app, but I have to break it off with you.. you are becoming more controlling with each passing day. First it was just a suggestion to take a relaxing bath, but now you\'re insisting that I enjoy a spinach and strawberry salad and take my sweetie to my favorite tapas bar? I don\'t even HAVE a favorite tapas bar, I\'m convinced I\'ll never be able to live up to your standards. This is goodbye and good riddance, I will never again allow you to dictate how I should live my life.
